# closure of the canonical gRPC service framework ecosystem spanning the
# three major systems languages, with a beautiful Buf Connect protoc-plugin
# pairing across Go and TypeScript:
#
#     Rust    : tonic              by the tokio team (async gRPC over hyper+h2
#                                    with Tower middleware integration)
#                 → volo (CloudWeGo/ByteDance Rust RPC framework scaffolding)
